          "<span class=\"first-chapter-phrase\"><span class=\"first-in-chapter character-a\">A</span>bu Abdullah</span><sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The fever goes out (is cured) in three (ways) – The sweating, and the excretion and the vomiting’."
